    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Keep your tools handy while gold prospecting with the ASR Outdoor Utility Belt! This belt comes with 3 pockets, a zipper pouch and a heavy duty buckle. The pouch is constructed of 600 Denier durable nylon and the belt adjusts 38&quot; - 48&quot;. The belt also comes with 2 3&quot; carabiners and an elastic band at the top of the pouch for holding miscellaneous items. It is perfect for holding metal detectors, home improvement or craft tools. Make sure to grab one of these before your next gold prospecting trip!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 11&quot; Utility Belt and Pouch Heavy Duty Nylon 3 Pockets Carabiners</h2>\n  <p>Keep your tools handy while gold prospecting with the ASR Outdoor Utility Belt!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Overall Pouch Size:</strong> 11&quot; x 11.5&quot;</li>\n    <li><strong>Material:</strong> 600 Denier Nylon</li>\n    <li>Belt Adjusts 38&quot; - 48&quot;</li>\n    <li>Pockets of Various Sizes for Versatility</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/gold_panning/accessories/GP3-45CP_Main.jpg\" alt=\"Keep your tools handy while gold p